OL,3,CMerseyside prisons top list of most
OL,4,Cinmates released early say new figures
OL,6,FPrisons on Merseyside accounted for
OL,7,Fthe largest number of prisoners
OL,8,Freleased early under a scheme
OL,9,Fintroduced by the former Conservative
OL,10,FGovernment.
OL,12,FThe scheme, known as End of Custody
OL,13,FSupervised Licence (ECSL), continued
OL,14,Ffor a few months after the
OL,15,FConservatives lost the general
OL,16,Felection in July this year.
