OL,3,CMerseyside prisons top list of most
OL,4,Cinmates released early say new figures
OL,6,FIt was superseded in September by a
OL,7,Fseparate early release programme
OL,8,Fintroduced by the new Labour
OL,9,FGovernment which has already seen
OL,10,Fthousands of inmates freed under
OL,11,Fdifferent terms.
OL,13,FFigures from the Ministry of Justice
OL,14,Fshow that HMP Liverpool accounted for
OL,15,Fthe largest number of prisoners
OL,16,Freleased with 402.
OL,18,FHMP Altcourse in Merseyside had the
OL,19,Fnext highest release figures with 396,
OL,20,Ffollowed by HMP Cardiff with 386 and
OL,21,FHMP Humber with 339.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
