OL,3,CMerseyside prisons top list of most
OL,4,Cinmates released early say new figures
OL,6,FIn all more than 13,000 prisoners in
OL,7,FEngland and Wales were released early
OL,8,Funder the scheme.
OL,10,FThe move is likely to have contributed
OL,11,Fto a sharp rise this year in the
OL,12,Fnumber of offenders recalled to
OL,13,Fcustody for breaching the conditions
OL,14,Fof their release.
OL,16,FSome 13,325 prisoners were released
OL,17,Fearly between October 17 2023 and
OL,18,FSeptember 9 2024, according to data
OL,19,Fpublished by the Ministry of Justice
OL,20,F(MoJ).
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
