OL,3,CMerseyside prisons top list of most
OL,4,Cinmates released early say new figures
OL,6,FJust over a quarter (26%) of those
OL,7,Freleased under the ECSL scheme had
OL,8,Fbeen found guilty of an offence
OL,9,Fclassed as violence against the
OL,10,Fperson, a similar proportion (26%) had
OL,11,Fbeen convicted of a theft offence,
OL,12,Fwhile nearly one in seven (15%) had
OL,13,Fbeen jailed for drug offences.
OL,15,FNo prisoners serving time for a sexual
OL,16,Foffence were released.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
