OL,4,Cinmates released early say new figures
OL,6,FRishi Sunak's administration insisted
OL,7,Fthe measure would be temporary and
OL,8,Fonly apply to "low-level offenders" as
OL,9,Fit sought to justify the plan by
OL,10,Fblaming problems with jails reaching
OL,11,Fcapacity on backlogs exacerbated by
OL,12,Fthe coronavirus pandemic and the 2022
OL,13,Fbarristers' strike.
OL,15,FBut, at the time, prisons watchdog
OL,16,FCharlie Taylor branded the situation
OL,17,F"entirely predictable" as he raised
OL,18,F"serious concerns" about the move
OL,19,Fwhich initially saw some prisoners in
OL,20,Fcertain jails released 18 days early.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
