OL,3,CMerseyside prisons top list of most
OL,4,Cinmates released early say new figures
OL,6,FThis was increased in March 2024 to a
OL,7,Fmaximum of 35 days and then again in
OL,8,FMay, which eventually saw criminals
OL,9,Fbeing freed from jail up to 70 days
OL,10,Fbefore their release date.
OL,12,FSeparate figures published on Thursday
OL,13,Fshow there were 9,782 recalls to
OL,14,Fcustody in April to June 2024 of
OL,15,Foffenders who had breached the
OL,16,Fconditions of their release, up 44%
OL,17,Ffrom 6,814 in the equivalent period in
OL,18,F2023.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
