OL,3,CMerseyside prisons top list of most
OL,4,Cinmates released early say new figures
OL,6,FThe figures also show the total number
OL,7,Fof prisoners in England and Wales
OL,8,Frecalled to custody for breaching
OL,9,Fconditions of their release stood at
OL,10,F12,579 on September 30 2024, up 5%
OL,11,Fyear on year and a "record high" for
OL,12,Fthe end of a calendar month, the MoJ
OL,13,Fadded.
OL,15,FOf the 13,325 prisoners released early
OL,16,Funder the ECSL scheme, 35% were
OL,17,Fserving a sentence of six months or
OL,18,Fless, while 16% had a sentence between
OL,19,Fsix and 12 months, according to
OL,20,Fanalysis by the PA news agency.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
