OL,6,FThis means just over half of those
OL,7,Freleased (51%) had a jail sentence of
OL,8,Fless than a year.
OL,10,FA further 16% had a sentence of 12
OL,11,Fmonths to less than two years, 18% had
OL,12,Fa jail term of two years to less than
OL,13,Ffour years, and 14% were serving
OL,14,Fsentences of four years of more.
